" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 480px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Comparison of dapsone (a sulfone) and sulfonamide structures",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 460px; height: 363px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Dapsone is a sulfone medication, rather than a sulfonamide. Dapsone can cause hypersensitivity reactions that are clinically similar to those caused by sulfonamides, however.",
"    <br>",
"     <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"      * R: substituted aromatic ring.",
